                	<i class="fas fa-redo fa-icon text-[var(--accent-blue)] text-2xl"></i>
                	<p class="text-lg text-[var(--text-light)] bg-[#FFE7C4] px-2 py-1 rounded" data-i18n="resilience-highlight">Failure isn’t the end of the road — it’s part of the process.</p>
            	</div>
            	<p class="text-base text-[var(--text-light)]" data-i18n="resilience-body">When a project doesn’t succeed, I don’t walk away. I re-learn, analyze what went wrong, identify weaknesses, and resolve them with targeted solutions. <em>Why did it fail? What can be rebuilt?</em> Then, I try again — testing, refining, and iterating until success becomes inevitable. For me, it’s not just about building projects. It’s about building better versions of myself along the way.</p>
        	</div>
